*   Browse popular movies.
*   Browse trending movies.
*   Search for specific movies.
*   View movie details (title, overview, release date, rating).
*   Receive basic personalized recommendations.
*   Responsive design (basic styling included).



*   [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) installed
*   [npm](https://www.npmjs.com/) or [yarn](https://yarnpkg.com/) installed


1.  Clone this repository:
    ```bash
    git clone <repository-url>
    cd movie-recommendation-app
    ```

2.  Install dependencies:
    ```bash
    npm install
    # or
    yarn install
    ```

3.  **Obtain a TMDB API Key:**
    *   Sign up or log in at [The Movie Database (TMDB)](https://www.themoviedb.org/).
    *   Go to your account settings and navigate to the API section.
    *   Request an API key.
    *   Replace `'YOUR_TMDB_API_KEY'` in `src/api/tmdb.js` with your actual key.


Start the development server: